{"tid":1740371,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"瞓醒覺出嚟強烈譴責了","createTime":"2019-11-20T02:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T03:30:12.000Z","uid":74622,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5d64641e07a331130c675a09a0c2be64c5906a2f","tid":1740371,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uc0bX3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuc0bX3w.png&h=f2ad6ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一早講咗會有哩條條例<br />\n<br />\n你哋班狗仲要得寸進尺<br />\n<br />\n要怪就怪班狗 我哋有幾多手足犧牲"},{"pid":"7355d6848051021f9bc6d3b809226ce3d9713612","tid":1740371,"uid":95138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:06:37.000Z","msg":"手足用血汗換返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ffb2e577f5c484d629959f7d50269512b4a333","tid":1740371,"uid":74622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7355d6848051021f9bc6d3b809226ce3d9713612","tid":1740371,"uid":95138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:06:37.000Z","msg":"手足用血汗換返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzJAFjm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzJAFjm.png&h=fe3f541c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7e67d126d6ce44d712cc9c1e1ddc36c62971898","tid":1740371,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:09:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">［請廣傳］和理非目前可以做到嘅事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.）建議香港人即時停止再月捐所有喺今次革命奶共/ 無幫過香港人嘅NGO組織（例如：無國界醫生、樂施會、宣明會）將啲錢用喺更加有用嘅地方上面，例如揸車接放學嘅油費、飯券、法庭訟費、醫療開支、FA嘅物資費用等等<br />\n<br />\n2.）本地文宣上，各區連儂牆近日被大肆清拆，各位香港人可以喺朝早人多時份重建連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n3.）持續喺國際文宣上着力，呼籲國際社會支持香港示威者五大訴求"},{"pid":"f23143055d8d12a4273cc253c9c7e954b77d3646","tid":1740371,"uid":247817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"呢幾隻字聽過十萬九千次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e235314d8d00561ff0120348f267194bc252085e","tid":1740371,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:10:46.000Z","msg":"美國內政不容許中國說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8b239f3ca15d51c85aeb382554a9797ba9c7a9","tid":1740371,"uid":211466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"人地國家抵制你D 人, 係人地國家事務, 關你大陸閪事咩"},{"pid":"aa35ee86cde0367dad4d646e4ebb1fe214e000b4","tid":1740371,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:11:36.000Z","msg":"#讀者投稿 #被捕支援<br />\n<br />\n有好多手足被捕後都會送入醫院，但當中有部分係無落名登記<br />\n(Registered as NE9，Unknown name Unknown ID in AED)<br />\n<br />\n意味住，被消失都無人知<br />\n<br />\n現呼籲被捕人仕嘅親友去醫院，話收到消息仔女入左黎，但無帶身份證，講晒啲資料，逼詢問處既人搵case<br />\n<br />\n被捕人士關注組有持續更新手足入院嘅情況:exclamation:(Poly嗰啲搵唔到嘅可以去廣華/屯門/將軍澳碰運氣)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=0b47584c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a>"},{"pid":"74517850b51eb4f69b9456cfad9c9ec0b6e624f3","tid":1740371,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"敵人反對嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3664a0ad325d692420d5dd0d1c36f04e56a70b1","tid":1740371,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74517850b51eb4f69b9456cfad9c9ec0b6e624f3","tid":1740371,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"敵人反對嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:15:18.000Z","msg":"証明方向正確"},{"pid":"8be25e387305a574dc7b2def78db5cc2f82f6ede